Fix/pdf tool flag (#44)

**Fix - allow AgentX to run without SQL & pdf tools**
(i.e. with `PDF_TOOL_ENABLED="false"` and `SQL_TOOL_DB_ENABLED="false"` in `.env`)
1) **Issue summary:** error starting up the app without pdf tool
2) **Steps to reproduce:** set your .env with pdf and SQL tool off, make sure to remove those tools from the agent actions.
3) **Expected vs what happened**: An agent without unneeded tools should start-up smoothly, but instead the app wasn't able to start.
4) Any notes on **why you think this might be happening**: tools are initiated by default, without checking the env.
